Description: Computes approximated adjusted fractional Bayes factors for
    equality, inequality, and about equality constrained hypotheses.
    For a tutorial on this method,
    see Hoijtink, Mulder, Van Lissa, and Gu (2019) <doi:10.1037/met0000201>.
    For applications in structural equation modeling, see 
    Van Lissa, Gu, Mulder, Rosseel, Van Zundert, and Hoijtink (2020)
    <doi:10.1080/10705511.2020.1745644>.
    The statistical underpinnings are
    explained in 
    Gu, Mulder, and Hoijtink (2018) <doi:10.1111/bmsp.12110>,
    Hoijtink, Gu, and Mulder (2018) <doi:10.1111/bmsp.12145>, and
    Hoijtink, Gu, Mulder, and Rosseel (2018) <doi:10.1037/met0000187>.
